review: These Rannsgeer 1/4 inch TRS to 1/4 inch TRS right angle patch cables are a fantastic addition to my setup. The high-density braided copper shield and gold-plated connectors ensure reliable performance and minimize signal loss, which is crucial for maintaining sound quality. The flexible rubber jacket makes them easy to manage and store without tangling, and the 6-foot length is perfect for connecting various audio equipment. The build quality is solid, and they have performed flawlessly in both studio and live settings. Highly recommend!
